						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab standing in Hanumān temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>12th-13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th-13th Century A.D.,</hi> seems to register a gift of land. The extant portion of the date refers to <hi rend="bold">Puṇṇami, Monday,</hi> all other details being lost.</p>						

